commit.message: Make sure argument is string and not some Path or whatever. Fixes #417.
Detox is no longer maintained in favor of tox -p auto.

Python 2 has not been dropped yet

Python < 3.4 was not dropped in 2.6.0, as Python 2.7 is still supported. Fix this changelog typo to make things clear

Work with xdist 2.0

Fixes #411, at cost of support for xdist 1.22 and earlier from 2017.
Rework assertion to work on old pytest.
Implement better --no-cov warning: only do it if --no-cov is present before --cov. Also remove some legacy pytest support and bump min version in setup.py. Closes #407. Ref #304.
Skip horrendous breakage on pypy and windows.
More blissful ignorance (windows doesn't allow deleting while in cwd use).
Add fix for sloppy tests that mess with CWD and break coverage's internals. Fixes https://github.com/nedbat/coveragepy/issues/881. Closes #306.
Update pins and add a rtd config.
